hi, welcome to  monitor program, 
you can choose one thing to do: installing  or uninstalling .

A) Do you want install monitor program , OK? , Well , let's install it now .
   1) su -
   2) make install
   3) crontab -e 
    input: */1 * * * * /monitor/share/check_per_minute.sh

B) The monitor program is too bad, you can not bear it any more . Uninstalling is the best choice .
   1) su -
   2) make uninstall
   3) crontab -e
     del : */1 * * * * /monitor/share/check_per_minute.sh

